Text: HoustonChroniclecomIsnt it funny that the same people who would have been screaming the loudest about the immorality of Bill and Hilary Clinton had their daughter Chelsea been cited for underage drinking are the same people who now find the treatment of the Bush family so outrageous I cant stand Chuys because their food is too heavy but I plan to eat there every week just to offset the amazing level of hypocrisy I have seen in the several emails I have received related to this subject
